text:
One year ago today...

On March 11, 2020, the WHO officially declared #COVID19 a pandemic.

Since then, at least 2.62 million have died. 

We are still ~Oct/Nov 2020 in daily volume of new cases/deaths.

Stay vigilant. Stay safe. Please #MaskUp & take the #vaccine when available. https://t.co/yZcWfPxRKh
